  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2006",
  "title": "Support multiple Configure components?",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nBoth\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nRendering a second configure does nothing.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nFor the props to be merged into the search state\r\n\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\n\r\nI need to show a refinement for a search radius. This only gets shown once a location is selected, which sets a bounding box on the search state. Now the user can select one of three radius's which are added to a second configure with the prop `radius`. Is there a better way to add a radius refinement?\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n3.2.1",
